Package com.epam.controller.command

Class CommandNames

java.lang.Object
com.epam.controller.command.CommandNames
public final class CommandNames extends Object
The CommandNames class is a final class that contains the string constant names of various commands. These commands are used by the controllers to perform specific actions.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Hrebenozhko Ruslan
